      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 386,
      "message": "I'm concerned about this:\n- If this deletes some schema sets and then throws an exception, the next line (deleteDataNodes) will not execute.\n- When it falls back to individual delete, when it tries to deleteSchemaSetWithCascade on line 380, it would fail again with SchemaSetNotFoundException, because it was already deleted here.\n- This would result in schema set being deleted, but not data node.",
